rows.label: qst700402_msg0002
rows.name: Laura, stay back. I will open a path.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0004
rows.name:
Look around you. Are they the only
ones with numbers on their side?

rows.label: qst700402_msg0005
rows.name:
Don't make the wrong first move.
Don't become "alone" on your own.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0007
rows.name:
Hmph, I just don't want
to carry dead weight.

rows.label: qst700402_msg0008
rows.name: You're not very honest, are you?
